the%20age%20of%20geriatric%20millionaires%2C%20and%20it%20might%20point%20to%20overlapping%20issues%3A%20Younger%20workers%20can't%20amass%20wealth%20at%20the%20same%20rate%20they%20used%20to%2C%20and%20increasingly%2C%20the%20way%20to%20ascend%20to%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20wealthy%20is%20to%20receive%20inheritances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMulti-generational%20wealth%20is%20doing%20fine%2C%20but%20first-generation%20people%20who%20are%20not%20on%20the%20wealth%20train%20are%20having%20a%20harder%20time%20getting%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Chuck%20Collins%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20program%20on%20inequality%20and%20co-editor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Finequality.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einequality.org%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20left-leaning%20Institute%20for%20Policy%20Studies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20bad%20news%20for%20the%20American%20dream%20of%20hitting%20it%20big%20as%20a%20self-made%20entrepreneur.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fjemimamcevoy%2F2024%2F04%2F06%2Ftrust-fund-fortunes-the-worlds-richest-heirs-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20third%20of%20the%20people%20on%20its%20latest%20billionaire%20list%20inherited%20all%20or%20most%20of%20their%20wealth%3B%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.forbesimg.com%2Fmedia%2Flists%2F10%2F2001%2Fbillpdf.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2001%20ranking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20five%20out%20of%20the%20490%20ranked%20billionaires%20were%20listed%20as%20having%20inherited%20their%20wealth.%20And%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20those%20individuals%20are%20inheriting%20that%20wealth%20much%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20millionaires%20are%20aging%20and%20they're%20not%20passing%20that%20wealth%20down%20the%20generational%20line%20or%20they're%20passing%20it%20on%20much%20later%20in%20life.%20Even%20the%20recipients%20are%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%