t%20Chuck%20Collins%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Policy%20Studies%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BKing%20Charles%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20King%20Charles%20III%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20who%20ascended%20the%20throne%20at%20the%20age%20of%2073.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%2060-year-olds%20giving%20to%2030-year-olds%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%2090-year-olds%20giving%20to%2060-year-olds%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20that%20because%20these%20wealthy%20folks%20are%20holding%20onto%20wealth%20longer%2C%20that%20intergenerational%20wealth%20transfer%20that%20we've%20all%20heard%20about%20is%20later%20in%20life%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20different%20to%20inherit%20a%20couple%20million%20dollars%20when%20you're%20in%20your%20twenties%20than%20it%20is%20in%20your%20sixties.%20You've%20already%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20decisions%20in%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-age-millennials-inheriting-wealth-older-boomers-living-longer-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718442121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66689367e07904901817c7fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-age-millennials-inheriting-wealth-older-boomers-living-longer-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Millionaires%20have%20been%20getting%20older%2C%20and%20holding%20onto%20their%20wealth%20for%20longer.%20It's%20creating%20a%20King%20Charles%20effect.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-age-millennials-inheriting-wealth-older-boomers-living-longer-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DMK%20slams%20BJP-led%20g