0Magura%20drone%20seen%20here.%3Cp%3EGENYA%20SAVILOV%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETaiwan%20recently%20unveiled%20a%20kamikaze%20boat%20many%20times%20larger%20than%20Ukraine's%20successful%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENaval%20drones%20will%20be%20key%20if%20Taiwan%20hopes%20to%20defeat%20a%20Chinese%20invasion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20can%20succeed%20by%20showing%20China%20that%20a%20battle%20for%20Taiwan%20is%20simply%20too%20bloody%20and%20risky.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20a%20cue%20from%20Ukraine's%20use%20of%20naval%20drones%20to%20offset%20a%20superior%20Russian%20fleet%2C%20Taiwan%20has%20unveiled%20a%20much%20larger%20unmanned%20kamikaze%20boat%20that%20could%20devastate%20a%20Chinese%20amphibious%20force.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdef-ltn-com-tw.translate.goog%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F4693122%3F_x_tr_sl%3Dauto%26_x_tr_tl%3Den%26_x_tr_hl%3Den-US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETaiwanese%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20describe%20a%2020-ton%20robot%20vessel%20that's%2055-feet-long%2C%2012-feet-wide%2C%20and%20with%20a%20draft%20of%20about%203%20feet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20vessel's%20top%20speed%20exceeds%2030%20knots%20(55.56%20km%2Fh)%2C%20and%20it%20can%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20over%20300%20miles%20(555.6%20km)%20with%20a%20fuel%20capacity%20of%201%2C300%20liters%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Taiwan's%20Liberty%20Times%20newspaper.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20remarkable%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20navigate%20autonomously%2C%20even%20without%20GPS%20or%20communication%20equipment%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20advanced%20onboard%20computer%20systems.%20Its%20potential%20military%20applications%20range%20from%20mine%20clearance%20and%20minesweeping%20to%20suicide%20missions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unmanned%20surface%20vessel%2C%20or%20USV%2C%20was%20revealed%20June%202%20while%20Taiwanese%20leaders%20attended%20the%20shipyard%20christening%20of%20a%20new%20frigate%20and%20other%20manned%20vessels.%20Photographs%20show%20a%20low%2C%20streamlined%20black%20boat%20with%20bright%20orange%20stripes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20USV%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Buniversal%20test%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Taiwanese%20officials%20have%20not%20said%20whether%20this%20design%20will%20stay%20experimental%20or%20go%20into%20mass%20production%20to%20create%20a%20horde%20of%20robot%20explosive%20boats.%20But%20if%20not%20this%20one%2C%20Taiwan%20will%20certainly%20field%20some%20kind%20of%20unmanned%20attack%20boat%20to%20try%20to%20stop%20a%20Chinese%20invasion%20or%20blockade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20officials%20have%20already%20spoken%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-plans-turn-taiwan-strait-into-drone-hellscape-against-china-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3Bhellscape%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20strategy%20that%20would%20use%20drones%20to%20turn%20the%20Taiwan%20Straits%20into%20a%20graveyard.%20Exactly%20what%20this%20entails%20is%20classified.%20But%20Adm.%20Samuel%20Paparo%2C%20chief%20of%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2024%2F06%2F10%2Ftaiwan-china-hellscape-military-plan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20Washington%20Post%20reporter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20China's%20invasion%20fleet%20begins%20moving%20across%20the%20100-mile%20waterway%20that%20separates%20China%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20the%20US%20military%20would%20deploy%20thousands%20of%20unmanned%20submarines%2C%20unmanned%20surface%20ships%20and%20aerial%20drones%20to%20flood%20the%20area%20and%20give%20Taiwanese%2C%20US%20and%20partner%20forces%20time%20to%20mount%20a%20full%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20turn%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20into%20an%20unmanned%20hellscape%20using%20a%20number%20of%20classified%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Paparo%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20I%20can%20make%20their%20lives%20utterly%20miserable%20for%20a%20month%2C%20which%20buys%20me%20the%20time%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20threat%20to%20attack%20a%20Chinese%20invasion%20force%20right%20away%20may%20not%20be%20achievable%2C%20however.%20In%20May%2C%20China's%20military%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-showed-how-easily-no-notice-it-can-surround-taiwan-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurrounded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Taiwan%20and%20practiced%20attack%20drills%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20large-scale%20exercise%20that%20could%20become%20cover%20for%20a%20military%20operation%20like%20a%20beach%20assault.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaiwan%20may%20have%20better%20luck%20in%20the%20water%20than%20in%20the%20air.%20Taiwan's%20attempt%20to%20develop%20a%20medium-altitude%2C%20long-endurance%20drone%20%E2%80%94%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20US%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20%E2%80%94%20has%20run%20into%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Funmanned%2F2024%2F03%2F27%2Famid-faltering-domestic-program-taiwan-orders-more-mq-9b-drones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edevelopmental%20difficulties%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20unmanned%20aircraft%20has%20yet%20to%20pass%20its%20combat%20readiness%20test%2C%20leading%20Taiwan%20to%20order%20more%20American-made%20MQ-9B%20SeaGuardians%2C%20a%20maritime%20version%20of%20the%20Reaper.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Taiwan%20and%20America%20are%20looking%20to%20what%20has%20become%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20naval%20drone%20warfare%3A%20Ukraine's%20campaign%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea.%20Vastly%20outnumbered%20and%20outgunned%20by%20Russia's%20navy%2C%20and%20with%20a%20long%20coastline%20to%20defend%2C%20Ukraine%20could%20have%20been%20bled%20white%20trying%20to%20defend%20against%20Russian%20amphibious%20invasions%20and%20coastal%20bombardment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20Russia's%20Black%20Sea%20Fleet%20has%20retreated%20from%20Ukrainian%20waters.%20In%20part%20this%20is%20because%20of%20land-based%20anti-ship%20missiles%20such%20as%20the%20Neptune%2C%20which%20sank%20the%20cruiser%20and%20Black%20Sea%20Fleet%20flagship%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-moskva-sinking-wake-up-call-for-navies-experts-say-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMoskva%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202022.%20But%20mostly%20it's%20because%20of%20robot%20boats%20that%20have%20relentlessly%20stalked%20Russian%20warships%20on%20the%20sea%20and%20even%20in%20port.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-damages-two-small-russian-landing-boats-crimea-kyiv-says-2023-11-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENovember%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Ukrainian%20Magura%20sea%20drones%20sank%20or%20damaged%20two%20Russian%20landing%20craft%20and%20a%20missile%20corvette%20docked%20in%20Crimean%20ports%20and%20shipyards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-ukraine-war-sea-drones-explosives-1b0974b77e32d6b5e9409ba3451716c6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMagura%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20appears%20to%20be%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20Taiwanese%20USV%2C%20at%20about%2018%20feet%20long.%20It%20weighs%20about%20a%20ton%2C%20can%20carry%20a%20400-pound%20warhead%2C%20and%20had%20a%20range%20of%20500%20miles%2C%20with%20batteries%20sufficient%20for%2060%20hours%20of%20operation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20asymmetric%20warfare%3A%20though%20vastly%20outnumbered%20in%20conventional%20military%20resources%2C%20Ukraine%20turned%20to%20cheap%20alternatives%20that%20could%20be%20manufactured%20by%20its%20own%20domestic%20arms%20industry%20and%20exploited%20the%20enemy%20fleet's%20vulnerability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaiwan%20faces%20a%20similar%20dilemma.%20With%20a%20population%20of%20just%2024%20million%20compared%20to%20China's%201.4%20billion%2C%20and%20vastly%20less%20resources%20and%20manufacturing%20capacity%2C%20Taiwan%20probably%20can't%20prevail%20in%20a%20straight-up%20naval%20battle%20with%20Chinese%20naval%2C%20air%20and%20missile%20forces%2C%20not%20even%20with%20the%20help%20of%20allies%20Japan%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20win.%20It%20can%20succeed%20by%20showing%20China%20that%20a%20battle%20for%20Taiwan%20is%20simply%20too%20bloody%20and%20fraught%20with%20risk.%20Taiwan%20would%20need%20to%20sink%20or%20damage%20enough%20transport%20vessels%20that%20near%20the%20island%20to%20make%20a%20beach%20landing%20or%20blockade%20untenable.%20With%20insufficient%20troops%2C%20heavy%20weapons%20and%20supplies%20ashore%2C%20the%20beachhead%20would%20be%20vulnerable%20to%20being%20swept%20into%20the%20sea%20by%20a%20Taiwanese%20counterattack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20enough%20kamikaze%20drones%20could%20force%20China's%20large%20fleet%20farther%20off-shore%20in%20hopes%20of%20creating%20openings%20for%20air%20drops%20of%20supplies%20from%20Taiwan's%20allies.%20Even%20then%2C%20China%20may%20have%20the%20sheer%20fleet%20size%20to%20strangle%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20shows%20that%20drones%20will%20be%20an%20essential%20and%20low-cost%20way%20to%20stave%20off%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20w