20leader%20and%20prominent%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20-%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmohan-bhagwat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMohan%20Bhagwat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20boss%20of%20ruling%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20are%20expected%20to%20meet%20this%20afternoon%20in%20Gorakhpur%2C%20which%20is%20the%20latter's%20Assembly%20bastion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20-%20sources%20call%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bcourtesy%20meet%26quot%3B%20as%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20is%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20constituency%20for%20an%20unrelated%20event%2C%20is%20to%20take%20place%20either%20between%202%20and%204%20pm%20or%20after%20the%20latter's%20visit%20to%20the%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%20at%204.15%20pm.%20Whenever%20it%20does%20happen%2C%20however%2C%20it%20will%20take%20place%20amid%20hushed%20talk%20of%20a%20rift%20between%20party%20and%20mentor%2C%20which%20has%20been%20firmly%20denied%20by%20both%20camps.%20The%20Adityanath-Bhagwat%20meeting%20will%20also%20take%20place%20as%20reports%20circulate%20of%20a%20split%20within%20the%20BJP%20itself%2C%20over%20poor%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%20of%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20meeting%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20are%20significant%20after%20the%20former's%20speech%20this%20week%20in%20Nagpur%3B%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20seemed%20to%20express%20displeasure%20at%20the%20way%20the%20BJP%20(though%20he%20did%20not%20name%20the%20party)%20conducted%20its%20election%20campaign.%20He%20also%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20%3Cem%3Esevak%3C%2Fem%3E%20should%20serve%20without%20arrogance%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20remark%20many%20saw%20as%20directed%20at%20a%20top%20BJP%20leader%2C%20possibly%20even%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcompetition-not-war-mohan-bhagwat-on-election-running-parliament-5860771%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%2C%20Not%20War%26quot%3B%3A%20RSS%20Boss%20Bhagwat%20On%20Election%2C%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20RSS%20chief's%20comment%20was%20veiled%2C%20his%20colleague%20Indresh%20Kumar's%20was%20not%3B%20he%20slammed%20the%20%26quot%3Bparty%20which%20did%20bhakti%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20(a%20reference%20to%20building%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20UP's%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20seal%20a%20landslide%20win%20for%20the%20party)%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20moved%20quickly%20to%20dispel%20talk%20of%20a%20split%20with%20its%20political%20unit%3B%20sources%20said%20the%20message%20was%20just%20a%20pick-me-up%20for%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership%20and%20claimed%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20not%20much%20difference%26quot%3B%20to%20talks%20he%20gave%20after%20wins%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20The%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B%20remark%20was%20not%20directed%20at%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspeculation-rss-sources-on-talk-of-rift-with-bjp-after-chiefs-remarks-5891422%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSpeculation%26quot%3B%3A%20RSS%20Sources%20On%20'Rift'%20With%20BJP%20After%20Chief's%20Remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20for%20Indresh%20Kumar's%20jab%2C%20RSS%20sources%20distanced%20the%20organisation%20from%20the%20comments%20and%20sought%20to%20flip%20it%2C%20declaring%20Lord%20Ram%20%26quot%3Bstopped%20those%20(the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc)%20who%20became%20arrogant%26quot%3B%20at%20241.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-row-rss-leader-indresh-kumars-damage-control-after-arrogant-dig-at-bjp-5893755%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAfter%20Uproar%20Over%20%26quot%3BArrogant%26quot%3B%20Dig%20At%20BJP%2C%20RSS%20Leader's%20U-Turn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20the%20BJP%20had%20set%20itself%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20370%20seats%20(400%2B%20with%20allies)%20to%20form%20a%20third%20consecutive%20union%20government%20with%20a%20brute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20hobbled%20by%20a%20strong%20showing%20by%20the%20INDIA%20group%2C%20and%20pushback%20over%20policy%20issues%2C%20the%20party's%20previously%20formidable%20election-winning%20machinery%20managed%20only%20240%20seats%20-%2032%20below%20the%20majority%20mark%20-%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20rely%20on%20'kingmakers'%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20to%20complete%20its%20hat-trick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20decidedly%20sub-par%20showing%20was%20underlined%20by%20an%20abysmal%20result%20from%20UP%2C%20which%20the%20party%20has%20swept%20in%20every%20major%20election%20since%202014.%20The%20BJP%20won%20only%2033%20of%20the%20state's%2080%20seats%20after%20amassing%2071%20in%20the%202014%20poll%20and%2062%20in%20the%202019%20exercise.%20Rivals%20Samajwadi%20Party%20-%20a%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20-%20picked%20up%2037%2C%20its%20best%C2%A0general%20election%20result%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20claimed%20six%2C%20double%20its%20last%20two%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20speculation%20the%20BJP's%20shocking%20UP%20showing%20was%20fueled%20as%20much%20by%20discontent%20among%20farmers%20still%20protesting%20for%20MSP%2C%20as%20by%20concerns%20over%20unemployment%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20BJP's%20UP%20defeat%20is%20underlined%20by%20the%20fact%20it%20also%20the%20Faizabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20which%20includes%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20party's%20Ram%20Temple%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20abject%20results%20in%20other%20states%20too%20-%20like%20Bengal%2C%20where%20it%20lost%20six%20seats%20to%20rivals%20Trinamool%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20it%20was%20routed%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20is%2C%20however%2C%20to%20hold%20meetings%20to%20discuss%20the%20results%2C%20including%20claiming%20a%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Kerala%2C%20a%20state%20that%20has%20traditionally%20and%20comprehensively%20rejected%20the%20BJP.%20The%20party%20won%20Thrissur%20thanks%20to%20actor-politician%20Suresh%20Gopi%2C%20who%20has%20since%20been%20made%20a%20junior%20Union%20Tourism%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718439060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fv5gb8q7o_mohan-bhagwat-and-yogi-adityanath_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohan-bhagwat-yogi-adityanaths-big-meet-today-amid-rss-bjp-rift-buzz-5895411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20-%20a%20senior%20leader%20and%20prominent%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20-%20and%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20boss%20of%20ruling%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20are%20expected%20to%20meet%20this%20afternoon%20in%20Gorakhpur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohan-bhagwat-yogi-adityanaths-big-meet-today-amid-rss-bjp-rift-buzz-5895411%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohan-bhagwat-yogi-adityanaths-big-meet-today-amid-rss-bjp-rift-buzz-5895411%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohan-bhagwat-yogi-adityanaths-big-meet-today-amid-rss-bjp-rift-buzz-589