mg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111014919.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20decision%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20plea%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20followers%20of%20the%20Pustimargi%20sect%2C%20who%20argued%20that%20the%20film%20could%20disrupt%20public%20order%20and%20incite%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Niharika%20Lal%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Aamir%20Khan%20Son's%20Film%20Halted%2C%20An%201862%20Case%20And%20PM%20Modi's%20Old%20Blog%20On%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20annals%20of%20India's%20legal%20history%2C%20few%20cases%20have%20had%20as%20profound%20an%20impact%20as%20the%201862%20Maharaj%20Libel%20Case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20landmark%20case%20saw%20Karsandas%20Mulji%2C%20a%20fearless%20journalist%20and%20social%20reformer%2C%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20the%20powerful%20religious%20establishment%20of%20the%20Vallabhacharya%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20'Maharaj'%2C%20the%20launch%20film%20of%20Junaid%20Khan%2C%20Aamir%20Khan's%20son%2C%20whose%20release%20by%20Netflix%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulji's%20bold%20accusations%20of%20misconduct%20against%20Jadunathji%20Maharaj%2C%20a%20revered%20spiritual%20leader%2C%20played%20in%20the%20film%20by%20Jaideep%20Ahlawat%2C%20sparked%20a%20sensational%20trial%20that%20captivated%20the%20nation.%20The%20spiritual%20leader%20was%20accused%20of%20exploiting%20his%20female%20devotees%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20he%20praised%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20in%20a%20blog%20post%2C%20acknowledging%20his%20contributions%20to%20social%20reform%20and%20the%20bravery%20he%20exhibited%20during%20the%20Maharaj%20Libel%20Case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20highlighted%20Karsandas%20Mulji's%20dedication%20to%20truth%20and%20justice%2C%20emphasising%20how%20his%20legacy%20continues%20to%20inspire%20his%20efforts%20towards%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20public%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fma%2Fsaluting-freedom-truth-3013%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20blog%20on%20Independence%20Day%20in%202010%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20chief%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20written%2C%20%26quot%3B...Social%20reformist%20and%20journalist%20Karsandas%20Mulji's%20newspaper%20too%20was%20titled%20%26quot%3BSatya-Prakash%26quot%3B.%20Gujarat%20has%20accepted%20the%20path%20of%20truth%20as%20its%20weapon%20to%20fight%20all%20forms%20of%20injustice%2C%20neglect%20and%20against%20those%20who%20try%20to%20defame%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20write%2C%20%26quot%3BSaanch%20ne%20ave%20na%20Aanch%26quot%3B%20(There%20is%20no%20ignominy%20in%20speaking%20the%20truth).%20%26quot%3BSatya%20Chhapre%20Chadi%20ne%20Pokarshe%26quot%3B%20(Truth%20will%20always%20emerge).%20%26quot%3BSatya%20No%20Jay%26quot%3B%20(Truth%20always%20triumphs).%20This%20only%20is%20our%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Karsandas%20Mulji's%20investigative%20journalism%20exposed%20the%20alleged%20exploitation%20of%20female%20devotees%2C%20the%20ensuing%20court%20battle%20highlighted%20the%20crucial%20role%20of%20the%20press%20in%20challenging%20entrenched%20power%20structures%20and%20promoting%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20story%20of%20a%20journalist's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20truth%20and%20the%20enduring%20legacy%20of%20a%20case%20that%20redefined%20the%20boundaries%20of%20religious%20and%20journalistic%20authority%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20slated%20for%20release%20on%20Netflix%20on%20June%2014%2C%20the%20film%20has%20faced%20opposition%20from%20followers%20of%20the%20Vaishnavite%20Pushtimargi%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20followers%2C%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20argue%20that%20the%20film%20misrepresents%20their%20religious%20practices%20and%20disrespects%20their%20beliefs.%20This%20prompted%20a%20petition%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20ordered%20the%20temporary%20stay%20on%20the%20film's%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharaj%20Libel%20Case%20of%201862%20was%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20Indian%20legal%20and%20social%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20Mulji%20published%20his%20accusations%20in%20his%20Gujarati%20weekly%20newspaper%2C%20'Satya%20Prakash'.%20Jadunathji%20Maharaj%2C%20in%20response%2C%20filed%20a%20libel%20suit%20against%20Mulji%20and%20the%20newspaper's%20publisher%2C%20Nanabhai%20Rustomji%20Ranina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%2C%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Bombay%2C%20garnered%20widespread%20public%20and%20media%20attention.%20Starting%20on%20January%2025%2C%201862%2C%20and%20concluding%20on%20March%204%2C%201862%2C%20the%20case%20saw%20extensive%20testimonies%20from%20various%20individuals%2C%20including%20missionaries%20and%20doctors%20who%20corroborated%20Mulji's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%2C%20delivered%20on%20April%2022%2C%201862%2C%20was%20a%20landmark%20victory%20for%20Mulji.%20The%20court%20recognised%20his%20role%20as%20a%20journalist%20in%20exposing%20wrongdoing%20and%20promoting%20moral%20integrity%20in%20society.%20Mulji%20was%20ordered%20to%20be%20compensated%20Rs%2011%2C500%20for%20his%20legal%20costs%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%20Rs%2013%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiberals%20and%20reformists%20across%20India%20celebrated%20the%20verdict.%20Mulji%20was%20hailed%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BIndian%20Luther%26quot%3B%2C%20after%20the%20Protestant%20reformer%20Martin%20Luther%2C%20for%20his%20courage%20in%20challenging%20corrupt%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20press%20freedom%20and%20the%20vital%20role%20of%20journalism%20in%20social%20reform.%20It%20also%20led%20to%20increased%20scrutiny%20of%20religious%20figures%20and%20practices%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20controversy%2C%20the%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20the%20film's%20depiction%20of%20historical%20events%20could%20incite%20religious%20tensions%20and%20misinform%20the%20public%20about%20their%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court's%20decision%20to%20stay%20the%20film's%20release%20highlights%20the%20judiciary's%20role%20in%20balancing%20creative%20expression%20with%20societal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20have%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20case%2C%20noting%20the%20complexities%20involved%20in%20adjudicating%20matters%20related%20to%20artistic%20freedom%20and%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20must%20carefully%20consider%20the%20historical%20context%20and%20the%20filmmakers'%20intent%20while%20also%20ensuring%20that%20the%20portrayal%20does%20not%20lead%20to%20unrest%20or%20communal%20disharmony%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20lawyer%20and%20constitutional%20expert%2C%20Rajeev%20Dhavan.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718433180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fv6uem08_aamir-khan-with-son-junaid-khan_625x300_15_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-aamir-khans-son-junaid-khans-netflix-film-halted-an-1862-case-and-narendra-modis-old-blog-on-it-5894860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20release%20of%20the%20launch%20film%20of%20Junaid%20Khan%2C%20Aamir%20Khan's%20son%2C%20on%20Netflix%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20Gujarat%20High%20Court.%20In%20the%20annals%20of%20India's%20legal%20history%2C%20few%20cases%20have%20had%20as%20profound%20an%20impact%20as%20the%201862%20Maharaj%20Libel%20Case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalU