i%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EImplement%20certain%20apps%20and%20softwares%20to%20track%20mouse%20movements%20and%20activity.%20These%20tools%20will%20detect%20abnormal%20patterns%20that%20could%20signify%20the%20use%20of%20mouse%20jigglers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEducate%20employees%20on%20the%20risks%20of%20using%20mouse%20jigglers%20and%20implement%20policies%20against%20their%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20people%20use%20mouse%20jigglers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEmployees%20use%20mouse%20jigglers%20when%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20computers%20active%20during%20short%20breaks%20or%20interruptions%2C%20like%20bathroom%20visits%20or%20childcare%20duties%20while%20working%20remotely.%20This%20prevents%20the%20computer%20from%20showing%20them%20as%20inactive%20or%20entering%20sleep%20mode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20also%20comes%20in%20handy%20when%20they%20need%20uninterrupted%20time%20to%20read%20documents%20or%20complete%20tasks%20that%20require%20constant%20access%20to%20the%20file%20but%20they%20do%20not%20want%20their%20screen%20to%20go%20to%20sleep%20mode%20while%20they%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718431260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm4ae21dg_computer_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwells-fargo-fires-employees-over-mouse-jiggling-heres-what-it-means-5894560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mouse%20jigglers%20are%20software%20programs%20that%20automatically%20move%20the%20mouse%20cursor%20slightly%20and%20randomly%20to%20prevent%20a%20computer%20from%20going%20into%20sleep%20mode%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-