use-t20-world-cup-exit-sets-internet-ablaze-5894010%5C%22%3E'Azam%20Khan%20Won't%20Return%20To%20Pakistan%20Because...'%3A%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Exit%20Sets%20Internet%20Ablaze%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamim%20has%20been%20inconsistent%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20squad%20after%20the%20back%20injury%2C%20he%20was%20out%20of%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20and%20was%20also%20not%20selected%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20World%20Cup%20squad%2C%20citing%20a%20persistent%20back%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Tamim%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20Facebook%2C%20claiming%20he%20was%20not%20selected%20for%20the%20squad%20due%20to%20growing%20tension%20between%20him%20and%20BCB%20officials%20instead%20of%20not%20being%20fit%20enough%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20a%20documentary%2C%20while%20Tamim%20downplayed%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20relationship%20on%20the%20team%2C%20Shakib%20had%20a%20different%20perspective.%20%26quot%3BFor%20quite%20some%20time%20we%20were%20not%20talking%20a%20lot.%20%5BBut%5D%20it%20is%20not%20right%20that%20we%20were%20not%20on%20talking%20terms.%20The%20thing%20is%2C%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20used%20to%20be%20together%20all%20the%20time%20but%20that%20relationship%20was%20not%20there%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakib%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20the%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20natural...%20I%20got%20married%20and%20he%20got%20married%2C%20we%20were%20staying%20separately%20in%20different%20places%20and%20so%20there%20was%20very%20lesser%20time%20between%20us.%20We%20were%20staying%20in%20the%20same%20building%20in%20different%20floors%20%5Bearlier%5D%20so%20certainly%20that%20closeness%20starts%20to%20diminish%20as%20people%20start%20having%20separate%20family%20life%20and%20over%20time%20(the%20relationship)%20changed%20due%20to%20our%20busy%20schedules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib%20emphasised%20that%20despite%20the%20distance%2C%20their%20professional%20relationship%20remained%20intact.%20%26quot%3BLater%20what%20happened%20is%20that%20in%20the%20field%20when%20we%20met%2C%20we%20have%20spoken%20whenever%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20need%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20conversation%20between%20us%20apart%20from%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Read%20More%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshoaib-akhtars-one-line-post-goes-viral-after-pakistans-exit-from-t20-world-cup-5893922%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar's%20One%20Line%20Post%20Goes%20Viral%20After%20Pakistan's%20Exit%20From%20T20%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20underscored%20that%20their%20interactions%20were%20sufficient%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20team%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20extra%20efforts%20to%20bridge%20any%20perceived%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20like%20making%20it%20good%20or%20bad%20(as%20far%20as%20the%20relationship%20with%20Tamim%20is%20concerned).%20Till%20we%20played%20together%20and%20shared%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20incident%20took%20place%20that%20would%20harm%20the%20team.%20We%20tried%20to%20contribute%20whether%20we%20were%20talking%20or%20not%3B%20there%20was%20no%20kind%20of%20problem%20inside%20the%20field%20or%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakib%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20particularly%20controversial%20interview%20ahead%20of%20last%20year's%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20he%20accused%20Tamim%20of%20being%20irresponsible%2C%20Shakib%20clarified%20his%20intentions.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20try%20to%20give%20any%20message%20through%20that%20interview%20as%20it%20was%20certainly%20spontaneous.%20I%20felt%20that%20before%20going%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20I%20should%20clear%20everything%20so%20that%20people%20know%20what%20actually%20happened%20and%20why%20this%20kind%20of%20situation%20is%20created%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718431080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fegmeocco_tamim-iqbal-shakib-al-hasan-afp_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshakib-al-hasan-opens-up-on-rift-with-tamim-iqbal-says-bcb-chiefs-comments-created-this-situation-5884701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20star%20all-rounder%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20claimed%20that%20Bangladesh%20Cricket%20Board%20(BCB)%20Nazmul%20Hasan's%20comment%20ignited%20the%20rift%20between%20himself%20and%20Tamim%20Iqbal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshakib-al-hasan-opens-up-on-rift-with-tamim-iqbal-says-bcb-chiefs-comments-created-this-situation-5884701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshakib-al-hasan-opens-up-on-rift-with-tamim-iqbal-says-bcb-chiefs-comments-created-this-situation-5884701%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshakib-al-hasan-opens-up-on-rift-with-tamim-iqbal-says-bcb-chiefs-comments-created-this-situation-5884701%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Has%20Physics%20Wallah%20CEO%20Approached%20Supreme%20Court%20For%20Probe%20Into%20NEET%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlakh%20Pandey%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20prominent%20EdTech%20firm%20Physics%20Wallah%2C%20has%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20examination.%20This%20national-level%20entrance%20test%2C%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20and%20crucial%20for%20admissions%20into%20MBBS%20and%20other%20medical%20courses%2C%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20controversy%20over%20alleged%20irregularities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey's%20petition%20claims%20the%20alleged%20arbitrary%20awarding%20of%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20candidates%20by%20the%20NTA.%20He%20has%20requested%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20establish%20an%20expert%20panel%20to%20scrutinise%20the%20examination%20process%20and%20its%20results.%20The%20NEET-UG%202024%2C%20held%20on%20May%205%20across%204%2C750%20centres%2C%20saw%20participation%20from%20approximately%2024%20lakh%20candidates.%20While%20results%20were%20anticipated%20on%20June%2014%2C%20they%20were%20announced%20early%20on%20June%204%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20expedited%20answer%20sheet%20evaluations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControversy%20erupted%20following%20allegations%20of%20question%20paper%20leaks%20and%20the%20granting%20of%20grace%20marks%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20protests%20and%20legal%20challenges%20in%20seven%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20unprecedented%20performance%2C%20with%2067%20students%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20720%20-%20including%20six%20from%20a%20single%20centre%20in%20Haryana's%20Faridabad%20-%20has%20raised%20suspicions%20of%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2010%2C%20students%20gathered%20in%20Delhi%2C%20demanding%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20these%20allegations.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20contentious%20grace%20marks%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20top%20scorers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20examination%2C%20overseen%20by%20the%20NTA%2C%20is%20a%20gateway%20for%20medical%20admissions%20in%20both%20government%20and%20private%20institutions%20across%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20integrity%20of%20this%20year's%20process%20has%20been%20called%20into%20question%2C%20prompting%20protests%20and%20legal%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20uproar%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20assured%20aspirants%20and%20parents%20that%20there%20is%20no%20substantial%20evidence%20of%20a%20paper%20leak.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20under%20investigation%20by%20competent%20authorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20paper%20leak%20yet.%20There%20are%20allegations%20and%20competent%20authorities%20are%20looking%20into%20them.%20Certain%20allegations%20and%20loose%20information%20are%20coming%20in.%20Let%20us%20wait%20for%20the%20probe%20by%20the%20authorities%20concerned.%20Let's%20wait%20till%20July%208%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgment.%20There's%20nothing%20to%20hide...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20reassured%20students%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20delivered%20a%20judgment%20on%20the%20issue.%20He%20announced%20that%20all%201%2C563%20affected%20students%20would%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20reappear%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20the%20six%20centres%20where%20time%20constraints%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20measures%2C%20questions%20remain%20about%20the%20NTA's%20response%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20intervention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20not%20true.%20After%20the%20anomaly%20came%20to%20light%2C%20the%20NTA%20came%20up%20with%20a%20formula%20-%20the%20grace%20mark%20formula.%20It%20was%20cited%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20well.%20However%2C%20some%20anomalies%20were%20found%20in%20that%20formula%20because%20six%20students%20became%20the%20highest%20scorers%20on%20the%20list.%20That%20was%20an%20eyesore%20for%20many%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20delegation%20of%20students%20and%20parents%20met%20with%20Mr%20Pradhan%2C%20who%20urged%20them%20to%20trust%20the%20government's%20intentions%20and%20effort