0abundant%20in%20Central%20America%2C%20with%20fresh%20produce%20including%20watermelon%2C%20cantaloupe%2C%20pineapple%2C%20and%20mango%20served%20at%20nearly%20every%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20common%20mid-morning%20or%20afternoon%20snack%20to%20quickly%20boost%20energy%20levels%20and%20refresh%20yourself%20in%20the%20jungle%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20cut%20cantaloupe%20and%20watermelon%20on%20a%20table%20in%20the%20jungle%20of%20Costa%20Rica.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666cf177e07904901819639e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFruits%20including%20watermelon%2C%20cantaloupe%2C%20mango%2C%20and%20pineapple%20are%20served%20as%20an%20accompaniment%20to%20most%20meals%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%20%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFresh%20smoothies%20are%20also%20common%20throughout%20the%20country%20and%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20feel%20full%20without%20a%20heavy%20meal%20weighing%20you%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20already%20try%20to%20keep%20a%20bowl%20of%20cut%20fruit%20in%20the%20fridge%20for%20easy%20enjoyment%2C%20but%20my%20travels%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20reminded%20me%20to%20go%20beyond%20my%20staples%20of%20berries%20and%20bananas.%20While%20I%20can't%20get%20the%20same%20quality%20pineapple%2C%20even%20in%20sunny%20southern%20California%2C%20having%20some%20regularly%20can%20bring%20a%20little%20%3Cem%3Epura%20vida%20%3C%2Fem%3Eback%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220feb426-cde9-4abf-9f4d-56ae7414eff4%5C%22%3EPrioritize%20fish%20and%20chicken%20for%20protein%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20of%20traversing%20the%20country%2C%20we%20had%20to%20intentionally%20seek%20out%20red%20meat%20if%20we%20wanted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20locals%20prioritize%20fresh%20fish%20and%20chicken%20if%20they%20have%20a%20me