20of%20when%20the%20reigning%20monarch's%20actual%20birthday%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22King%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666866d7764df161125880cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKing%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%202023.%3Cp%3EChris%20Jackson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal.uk%2Fqueens-birthday%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20family's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20the%20chance%20of%20the%20weather%20being%20suitable%20for%20outdoor%20activities%20is%20higher%20in%20May%20or%20June.%20Considering%20much%20of%20the%20event%20takes%20place%20outside%2C%20scheduling%20it%20for%20the%20summer%20is%20easier.%20Nowadays%2C%20the%20event%20typically%20takes%20place%20on%20a%20Saturday%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fnews%2Fwhy-do-british-monarchs-have-two-birthdays%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHistory%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20King%20George%20II%20was%20the%20first%20monarch%20to%20move%20his%20birthday%20pageantry%20to%20the%20summer%2C%20as%20he%20was%20born%20in%20October%2C%20but%20he%20combined%20his%20official%20celebration%20with%20a%20summer%20military%20parade%20in%201748.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20monarch's%20actual%20birthday%20is%20publicly%20acknowledged%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal.uk%2Fgun-salutes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20royal%20gun%20salute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20sovereign%20typically%20celebrates%20privately%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2fa182e-7e24-44b0-8cdf-50c04b881a16%5C%22%3EA%20military%20parade%20is%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20the%20event%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%2C%20a%20parade%20of%20royals%20and%20military%20personnel%20travels%20from%20Buckingham%20Palace%20to%20the%20Horse%20Guards%20Parade%20at%20Whitehall%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20royal%20family's%20website%20states%20that%20the%20parade%20includes%20over%201%2C400%20soldiers%2C%20400%20musicians%2C%20and%20200%20horses%2C%20and%20the%20royals%20typically%20ride%20on%20horseback%20or%20in%20carriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20monarch%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20event%20from%20either%20carriage%20or%20horseback.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnewsround%2F43794588%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20rode%20a%20horse%20during%20the%20parade%20until%201987.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queen%20Elizabeth%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%201985.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66686582ed9a404d829c67e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQueen%20Elizabeth%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%201985.%3Cp%3EAnwar%20Hussein%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20parade%20reaches%20Whitehall%2C%20the%20monarch%20formally%20inspects%20the%20troops%20during%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20chosen%20Regimental%20Colour%2C%20or%20flag%2C%20is%20carried%20through%20the%20ranks%20of%20participating%20soldiers%20before%20they%20march%20back%20to%20Buckingham%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20onlookers%20cheer%20on%20the%20participants%20as%20they%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F1034322%2F20210713-FOI2021_06427_redacted_response_Redacted.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20FOIA%20request%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20the%202021%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%20cost%2059%2C662%20pounds%2C%20which%20would%20be%20approximately%20%2475%2C604%20today.%20That%20total%20includes%20stable%20costs%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20fuel%2C%20among%20other%20fees%2C%20though%20it%20does%20not%20factor%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20police%20presence%20required%20to%20keep%20the%20event%20safe%20for%20the%20royals%20and%20attendees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c860c09-d877-4936-a474-2eab118d03fe%5C%22%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20brings%20the%20royal%20family%20together%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20culminates%20in%20a%20flypast%20by%20RAF%20pilots%20over%20Buckingham%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flyover%20is%20arguably%20the%20most%20iconic%20moment%20of%20the%20event%2C%20as%20the%20royal%20family%20watches%20the%20planes%20go%20by%20from%20Buckingham%20Palace's%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20marks%20one%20of%20the%20few%20times%20a%20year%20the%20royal%20family%20gathers%20in%20one%20place%2C%20so%20they%20are%20always%20heavily%20photographed%20when%20they%20appear%20on%20the%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20occasion%20offers%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20how%20royals%20interact%20with%20each%20other%2C%20with%20people%20analyzing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrooping-the-colour-buckingham-palace-balcony-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshots%20of%20Princess%20Diana%20and%20Prince%20Harry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20years%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20royal%20family%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20during%20the%20Trooping%20of%20the%20Colour%20in%201989.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c52bd643bb77284ba50955%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221215%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20royal%20family%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20during%20the%20Trooping%20of%20the%20Colour%20in%201989.%3Cp%3EAnwar%20Hussein%2FGetty%20Image