f%201862.%20A%20significant%20legal%20battle%20in%20India's%20history%2C%20the%20case%20challenged%20religious%20authority%20and%20put%20focus%20on%20the%20role%20of%20journalism%20in%20social%20reform.%20It%20involved%20allegations%20of%20misconduct%20against%20a%20prominent%20spiritual%20leader%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BMaharaj%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20journalist%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20brought%20to%20light%20through%20his%20publication%2C%20'Satya%20Prakash'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharaj%20libel%20case%20was%20a%20big%20win%20for%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20who%20exposed%20wrongdoing%20in%20the%20Vallabhacharya%20sect.%20He%20was%20praised%20across%20India%20for%20his%20courage%2C%20and%20given%20the%20nickname%20of%20%E2%80%9CLuther%E2%80%9D%2C%20after%20Martin%20Luther%20King%2C%20for%20challenging%20corruption%20in%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20he%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20publicly%20praised%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20for%20his%20bravery%20and%20dedication%20to%20social%20reform.%20In%20a%20blog%20post%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20Mr%20Mulji's%20contributions%20and%20highlighted%20his%20commitment%20to%20truth%20and%20justice%2C%20reported%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film's%20narrative%2C%20centred%20on%20the%20sensitive%20event%2C%20drew%20objections%20from%20followers%20of%20the%20Vaishnavite%20Pustimargi%20sect%2C%20dedicated%20to%20God%20Shree%20Krishna%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20The%20followers%20argued%20that%20the%20film%20could%20distort%20their%20religious%20practices%20and%20provoke%20animosity.%20They%20moved%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%2C%20citing%20potential%20violations%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021%2C%20and%20self-regulation%20norms%20for%20OTT%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3