20of%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20bought%20their%20first%20computer%20in%202012%2C%20post%20which%2C%20the%20young%20boy%20would%20spend%20hours%20on%20the%20internet%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20hardware%2C%20networking%20and%20programming.%20He%20learnt%20from%20tutorials%20on%20Google%20and%20YouTube%2C%20following%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20late%20Kevin%20Mitnick%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20we%20can%20secure%20data%20for%20organisations.%20Even%20though%20companies%20have%20their%20own%20security%20teams%2C%20they%20invite%20ethical%20hackers%20to%20report%20vulnerabilities%20in%20their%20data%20through%20their%20responsible%20disclosure%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20343%20million%20people%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20cyber%20attacks%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Forbes%20report.%20Data%20breaches%20also%20saw%20a%2072%20percent%20increase%20in%202023%20compared%20to%202021%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20need%20for%20ethical%20hackers%20and%20cyber%20security%20experts%20all%20the%20more%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Class%2012%2C%20Muneeb%20pursued%20a%20B.Tech%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%20a%20college%20which%20was%2080%20km%20away.%20The%20daily%20travel%20and%20classes%20left%20him%20with%20no%20time%20to%20pursue%20his%20passion.%20Supported%20by%20his%20father%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20drop%20out%20in%20the%20second%20year%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20either%20complete%20my%20engineering%20degree%20or%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F231525%2Fcyfirma-startup-cybersecurity-chinese-hackers-india-cert-malware-phishing-dark-web-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20follow%20my%20passion%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20BCA%20degree%20in%20cyber%20security%20which%20also%20allowed%20me%20the%20time%20to%20hone%20my%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2022-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20pursuing%20BCA%20through%20correspondence%20from%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20National%20Open%20University%20(IGNOU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Muneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%20with%20his%20setup%20at%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMuneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%20with%20his%20setup%20at%20home%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Apple%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20user%20data%20leak%20on%20iCloud.%20I%20submitted%20my%20findings%20in%20July%202023%20and%20received%20an%20acknowledgement%20from%20them%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20developed%20his%20own%20interception%20tools%20that%20help%20him%20test%20data%20and%20find%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20family%20was%20initially%20hesitant%20about%20his%20choice%2C%20the%20growth%20of%20cybersecurity%20as%20a%20viable%20career%20option%20and%20the%20financial%20rewards%20doled%20out%20by%20companies%20for%20identifying%20breaches%20in%20their%20data%20helped%20convince%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20%E2%80%98bug%20bounties%E2%80%99%2C%20companies%20offer%20anywhere%20from%20%24100%20to%20%2410%2C000%20per%20vulnerability.%20The%20reward%20increases%20depending%20on%20the%20criticality%20of%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuneeb%20wishes%20to%20join%20a%20company%20as%20a%20cybersecurity%20analyst%20after%20completing%20his%20degree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20user%20data%20and%20company%20websites%20and%20domains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340888%2Fshark-tank-cybersecurity-app-artificial-intelligence-ai-pratyusha-vemuri-online-fraud-transactions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ethical%20hacking%20space%20is%20a%20growing%20one%20with%20multiple%20jobs%20opening%20up%20for%20the%20same%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20For%20anyone%20interested%20in%20getting%20into%20this%20space%2C%20more%20than%20degrees%2C%20Muneeb%20states%20that%20self-learning%20and%20knowledge%20about%20the%20hardware%2C%20operating%20systems%2C%20and%20networking%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20basic%20computer%20degree%20like%20a%20BCA%20or%20MCA%20or%20BTech%20would%20be%20good%20to%20enter%20into%20this%20field.%20Certifications%20like%20OSCP%20(Offensive%20Security%20Certified%20Professional)%20and%20CEH%20(Certified%20Ethical%20Hacker)%20will%20add%20value%20to%20your%20resume.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20is%20to%20learn%20about%20computer%20hardware%2C%20networking%2C%20operating%20systems%20like%20Linux%2C%20programming%20languages%2C%20coding%20languages%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%